text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha tae puok anak rngcham yeung kraw pi phl muoy nei phl la teangpir( slab sha hi t ryy chychomneah) nih ryy? haey puok yeung cham meul puok anak tha a l laoh nung thveu aoy puok anak chhucheab daoy tondakamm pi trong phtal ryy daoy dai phtal robsa puok yeung . dau che neah chaur puok anak rngcha choh pitabrakd nasa puok yeung ka rngcha cheamuoy puok anak der
